high_descs: Turn around, proceed to desk.
Pick up alarm clock from shelf directly below phone.
Turn right, proceed to bed.  Turn left to face nightstand.
Place alarm clock on nightstand directly behind the pencil.
Turn left, proceed to wall.  Turn right to face desk.
Pick up alarm clock from next to the cd.
Turn right, proceed to bed, turn left proceed to nightstand.
Put alarm clock on nightstand directly between the other alarm clock and the lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and take a big step forward then turn left and walk to the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk almost to the bed then turn left.
Put the alarm clock to the left of the lamp.
Turn around and walk a step then turn right and walk to the wall then turn right and walk to the desk.
Pick up the alarm clock that's in front of you.
Go back to where you put the first alarm clock.
Put this alarm clock on the table next to the first alarm clock.
anns.task_desc: Put two alarm clocks on the stand.

high_descs: Turn left and take one step, then turn left and walk to the desk.
Look down and take the clock from the shelf.
Turn right and walk to the bed, then turn left and walk to the bedside table.
Put the clock to the left of the lamp that is on the table.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn right.
Pick up the clock that is to the right of the CD.
Turn around and take one step, then turn left and walk to the bed, then turn left and walk to the bedside table.
Place the clock on the bedside table directly next to the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Put the clocks on the bedside table.
